  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Immediate Assistance for Flood &amp; Covid-19 Affected People in the Northern District of Jamalpur, Bang</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">People of Jamalpur district are severely affected by devastating monsoon flood and lost their livelihoods, damages houses and displaced to other places. People are suffering from food, water, shelter, hygiene materials, medicines, etc.</narrative>
  </description>
